hopobject.body: Until August zenerx official website Frazier, who began the 2012 season as the team’s starter and held that role through the first five games, offered to move into the defensive backfield after a meeting with Malzahn and offensive coordinator Rhett Lashlee. Both coaches sat down with Auburn’s quarterbacks over the weekend and confirmed that the race had narrowed to JUCO transfer Nick Marshall and freshman Jeremy Johnson, moving away from returnees Jonathan Wallace and Frazier.
